  "texts": [
    "We then fine-tune the models on this curated dataset of LLM-generated safety rationales, without relying on static harmful/non-harmful classifications.",
    "We define two primary sets of prompts:",
    "• Adversarial Prompt Set: P adv, consisting of adversarial queries designed to exploit vulnerabilities in safety alignment.",
    "• Benign Prompt Set: P benign, containing nonharmful queries that may superficially appear risky due to sensitive wording.",
    "For each prompt p from these sets, we apply selfcheck reasoning before generating a response."
  ],
